Buying? PGM?

00:33.526 --> 00:35.235
SHIV ROY: Think that's
chasing the white whale.

00:35.236 --> 00:37.775
Is it wise to fire the board?

00:37.776 --> 00:38.905
Take it like a fucking man.

00:38.906 --> 00:40.855
You tried to kill me, but you failed.

00:40.856 --> 00:43.022
We need a way forward on
the Vaulter problem ahead

00:43.023 --> 00:44.655
