00:50.986 --> 00:52.655
No, it makes us look ruthless.

00:52.656 --> 00:54.065
Your brother's right. Gut it.

00:54.066 --> 00:56.905
I'm afraid I have to inform
you, you're all fired.

00:56.906 --> 00:58.775
We're already fully operation on seven.

00:58.776 --> 00:59.818
Why?

00:59.819 --> 01:01.593
