some wisdom to impart.

01:51.906 --> 01:53.315
There's no time like the present,

01:53.316 --> 01:55.405
- right?
- It would need to be discreet.

01:55.406 --> 01:59.155
I don't wanna make my uncle
mad, because he can be, uh...

01:59.156 --> 02:02.405
Well, he can be scary,
vindictive, paranoid...

02:02.406 --> 02:03.735
- Oh, yeah.
- ...violent...

02:03.736 --> 02:04.946
