02:20.356 --> 02:21.446
But you did.

02:22.606 --> 02:26.275
Look, Greg, if you want
this to be anonymous,

02:26.276 --> 02:28.025
you have to say that from the outset.

02:28.026 --> 02:29.735
You can't do that retroactively.

02:29.736 --> 02:32.565
But no, because this isn't a meeting.

02:32.566 --> 02:33.945
- This... You can't...
- Look...

02:33.946 --> 02:36.025
- That's not fair. That's unfair.
- Greg,

02:36.026 --> 02:37.605
I am writing this biography.

02:37.606 --> 02:41.235
