Logan Roy's life and work.

02:41.236 --> 02:43.525
- Mm-hmm.
- And I really have no doubt

02:43.526 --> 02:46.065
that you have been to
a bunch of meetings,

02:46.066 --> 02:49.235
and you have done a bunch of things.

02:49.236 --> 02:51.316
So, my question is:

02:52.986 --> 02:57.025
