03:06.656 --> 03:08.855
Okay, I need to think.
I need... I'm gonna go,

03:08.856 --> 03:11.985
I... I'm... But this
leaving... How I look,

03:11.986 --> 03:13.855
and how I'm getting up and everything,

03:13.856 --> 03:15.355
