so Dad wants to buy it

08:31.236 --> 08:33.485
- to piss him off.
- KARL: What, for 20 billion?

08:33.486 --> 08:35.985
Well, can't he just take the
batteries out of his remote?

08:35.986 --> 08:38.275
Well, Pierce also own the New York Mail,

08:38.275 --> 08:39.735
