09:33.026 --> 09:36.565
Oh, yeah. No, no. I... I... I like it.

09:36.566 --> 09:37.905
- Good.
- Good.

09:37.906 --> 09:39.855
KENDALL: Okay. Good. Great.

09:39.856 --> 09:43.405
Let's, uh... Let's bag
this elephant for Dad.

09:43.406 --> 09:45.105
ROMAN: Yeah. Let's do it.

09:45.106 --> 09:47.236
Yeah. Let's bone this turkey.

09:51.276 --> 09:54.025
So, Pierce is the answer.

09:54.026 --> 09:55.655
Those blue-blooded fucks.

09:55.656 --> 09:58.735
