10:45.696 --> 10:47.315
- so...
- And pretty much your godfather,

10:47.316 --> 10:49.945
- and your closest business...
- KENDALL: Those are just facts.

10:49.946 --> 10:51.985
This is fuckin' bullshit. Jesus Christ.

10:51.986 --> 10:53.525
I think he knows he did bad.

10:53.526 --> 10:55.485
Oh, fuck. I swear to God, Dad,

10:55.486 --> 10:56.986
