11:43.066 --> 11:44.275
In my pants.

11:44.276 --> 11:45.815
ROMAN: Hey, is anyone in my house?

11:45.816 --> 11:48.656
Hey. Uh, have you seen this?

11:49.156 --> 11:50.235
