12:48.406 --> 12:49.815
He can do whatever the fuck he likes.

12:49.816 --> 12:51.985
He's like a human Saudi Arabia.

12:51.986 --> 12:55.905
So, what, you... you wanna
use Naomi to broker a deal?

12:55.906 --> 12:57.025
Bingo.

12:57.026 --> 12:58.985
